headline: Holland America Line Goes Glam with Cruising's First Lipstick Blending Bar at Sea
summary: Holland America Line is sailing into style with the launch of Blend Bar — the first lipstick blending bar at sea. Beauty connoisseurs can design and take home a signature lipstick or gloss created on board at the exclusive lipstick lab. The hands-on Blend Bar experience is guided by an expert beauty consultant who will help guests create a wearable memory of their cruise vacation.
